* Carnage eyed Cyber Claw, obviously she wasn't going to attack.
She looked back at Teltoli then at Cyber Claw...*

" Since the death of my best friend, Dinobot I've always wanted Megatron 
dead. Once I drop my friend off at the Maximal base I plan to hunt that 
tyrant down and rip him apart! Nobot slags my friends and gets away with 
it!"


* Carnage growled deeply and the spikes along her back bristled with 
aggression, she planed to keep that promise!*
